&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;BenchMark Physical Therapy, a brand partner of Upstream Rehabilitation, is looking for an Athletic Trainer to join our team in Jacksonville, NC serving the Onslow County Schools.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
